{"tid":1469482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼大法好","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:25:04.000Z","uid":133983,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6edfb2ab5d293936eadcaa210e48ce194f6ec2a","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"中共依下識玩啦　派個記者黎講明自己係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要驚你地太和理非唔打佢<br />\n派多幾個人帶頭<br />\n再加批衝動行事既示威者<br />\n分化勇武同和理非－－林鄭、警犬Ｄ記者會日日分化你地仲唔知目的？？<br />\n<br />\n破解大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實一向都話核彈都唔割<br />\n我絕對唔會為左一個已犯既錯割席<br />\n更何況動用私刑我係覺得無問題<br />\n但講明私刑就係私下了斷<br />\n你捉條友去殘廁gathering除佢褲<br />\n大大力錫佢春袋囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日綁起佢已經好足夠<br />\n應該即時沒收佢行裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncheck佢手機其他野有冇有用中共黑材料<br />\n然後未一齊睇下64呀、法輪大法好、新疆訓練營<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中港一家親！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5585c129c088a862426c3ca69424a0644910f14c","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f6497f1261559e2801a5b8626d63a376fac2a07","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e364886761887c4bacd4b95674104e26f613d802","tid":1469482,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c11d5851dde4051452f34436bf964c5e63b6574d","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0377ea40c0e242149c82413403a7bf6a7fa6b05a","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f9740a087b10e431a51ef4876e261381b097cc","tid":1469482,"uid":99801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"暴力有時候唔一定要以力制勝嘅。造成身體傷害都只係一時嘅事，又會招人話柄。<br />\n<br />\n其實圍住佢播d禁片，再一齊大大聲係耳邊屌9佢，做到4面楚歌嘅效果應該仲正，應該晚晚發惡夢都似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38716a8fdda3c6545f363fab0f2ffe4c00184c3","tid":1469482,"uid":133983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73f9740a087b10e431a51ef4876e261381b097cc","tid":1469482,"uid":99801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"暴力有時候唔一定要以力制勝嘅。造成身體傷害都只係一時嘅事，又會招人話柄。<br />\n<br />\n其實圍住佢播d禁片，再一齊大大聲係耳邊屌9佢，做到4面楚歌嘅效果應該仲正，應該晚晚發惡夢都似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"做敵人最怕既事<br />\n明知人地禁忌係咩仲唔圍住佢播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}